[The newswire reports a decrease in the number of dengue cases in Cambodia in the 1st 4 months of 2013 compared with the same period in 2012, although there was a report of an increase in the number of dengue cases in the 1st 3 months of 2013 in Cambodia, compared with the same period in 2012 (see PRO/MBDS posting Dengue - Cambodia 20130412.0768).

For a map of Cambodia with provinces, see http://ephotopix.com/image/asia/cambodia_province_map.gif. For the interactive HealthMap/ProMED-mail map with links to other recent PRO/MBDS and ProMED-mail postings on Cambodia and neighboring countries, see http://healthmap.org/r/1iGB. - Mod.QCN]

